Divorced and living alone in her mid 40s, nationally touring comedian Traci Kanaan didn’t want to face the possibility of living the rest of her life alone, so she did what millions of others have done and tried online dating. This book is a collection of the crazy and stupid emails Traci received via numerous online dating sites, and her hilarious responses (and non-responses) to the men "trying" to woo her.

Wings Hypnosis, LLC welcomes ALL people with an open heart and mind regardless of gender orientation, political views, religious affiliations, or belief systems. Hypnosis is a cooperative partnership between the client and the facilitator to create change in the conscious and subconscious space. Traci Kanaan is a Certified Clinical Hypnotherapist, Life and Lifestyle Coach, and Board Certified Medical Hypnotist. She is NOT a Licensed Medical Doctor or Mental Health Professional and does not portray herself as such. The Hypnosis and Hypnotherapy services performed are non-therapeutic and not intended to replace professional counseling, medical, or psychological care, and should not be used as a substitute for diagnosis or treatment of any condition. Traci Kanaan does not work on diagnosed mental or physical conditions without a referral from your licensed practitioner of the healing arts per Florida Statute Section 485. If you are under the care of a medical professional for any condition for which you are seeking hypnosis support, you must obtain and present a signed, written referral from your provider before contacting Traci and moving forward with sessions.
